beer.beer_description:
No way Jose - Mezcal Sour! 
Collaboration with Los Agaves 
Base beer of flaked corn and smoked malt.
Comes through with a subtle smokiness and then sweetness from the corn.
Smoked chilli salt and coriander seed added to the boil to achieve that classic salt & pepper gose characteristics but with a twist, adding just a touch of smoke & spiciness that only dances on the back of your pallet for a few seconds before dissipating.
Grapefruit, Lime and Mezcal added at the end of fermentation.
Super tart and refreshing. 
A lot of elements added but all are well balanced for a super smashable sour.
